1.Sentences start with "-" or capital letter.
2.Sentences end with "!", ".", "?".
3.Sentences are made of at least one word.
4.Words can contain only digits or only letters or only one special character "-"
5.Additionally, words can end with one of:",", "/", ";", ":", " " ",")", "}", "]"
6.Additionally, words can start with one of: "(" , "{", "[".
7.The brackets and the quotes must be open and closed with the corresponding one.
8. At the beginning and at the end of the line we don't have spaces.

